0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"為了使LIVE成功，逐步克服問題是理所當然的。\n放著問題不管站上舞台，是絕不可能發生","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event184-03-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"感覺，Roselia的過人之處\n似乎都濃縮在剛才那句話裡了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"嗚哇，有種出道LIVE又得表現得更好才行了的感覺……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event184-03-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"咦咦！？\n我沒有那個意思……抱，抱歉","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"啊哈哈，開玩笑的啦","ten